-> Use nvm to manage versions:
```bash
nvm install node      # latest
nvm use node
```

-> npm:
```bash
npm init -y           # create package.json
npm install express   # install package
npm install -g nodemon # global install
```

-> package.json structure:
```bash
{
  "name": "my-app",
  "version": "1.0.0",
  "main": "index.js",
  "scripts": {
    "start": "node index.js",
    "dev": "nodemon index.js"
  },
  "dependencies": {
    "express": "^4.18.2"
  }
}
```